sc_language - Create a new langauge.lproj bundle

USAGE:

  ./script/generate language client_name/languge_name [CLASS]

DISCUSSION:

This generator will create a new SproutCore language bundle.  You should pass as the first parameter your client directory name/the view you want to create.  For example:

./script/generate language todos/esperanto

creates a new lproj bundle esperanto.lproj in the client clients/todos.  This bundle will contain a strings.js that extends String. You should place your localized language translations here.